<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="trend-n">trend <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /trend/    美 /trend/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>趋向；趋势：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the general trend of history 
历史的总趋势</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Recently, we have seen a gradual <strong>trend towards</strong> healthier food. 
近来，我们注意到人们逐渐倾向于吃更加健康的食物。</p><footer>外研⑧ – 3</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>潮流：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the trend towards long hair 
流行长发</p></div></div>